    </figure><h3 class="title"><a href="/news/disturbing-footage-of-circus-animal-abuse-leads-to-widespread-reform-2/" data-click-tracking="genericClickCbsNews" data-omniture-track-data='{"clickProperty": "48 - 60 shared-Post-Reengagement|Asset-10-Headline"}'>Saving the Lions</a></h3>
	<p class="date">July 2, 2017</p>
        <p class="dek">
By secretly infiltrating circuses with hidden cameras, Animal Defenders International has helped protect and save the lives of wild animals around the world</p>

</div>





</li>            	        </ul></div>
